// Returns the contents of the file at the provided path
ReadFile(path string) (string, err)

// Returns the rendered template
RenderTemplate(template string, components map[string]string) (string, err)

// Returns the object contained in the provided yaml
ParseYaml(content string) (interface{}, err)
// Take into consideration that function might need to know at which location their current file resides. So an additional argument to pass around might be the Values object
